<text id="02-output-contract" title="C# Clean Architecture + CQRS Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the layered-solution manifest this methodology produces. Validator enforces required keys + per-field constraints.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/csharp-dotnet-patterns.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["solution_name", "projects", "use_cases", "arch_tests_pass", "outbox_configured"],
  "properties": {
    "solution_name": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[A-Z][A-Za-z0-9]+$"},
    "projects": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["Domain", "Application", "Infrastructure", "Api"],
      "properties": {
        "Domain": {"type": "object", "required": ["references"], "properties": {"references": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}, "maxItems": 0}}},
        "Application": {"type": "object", "required": ["references"], "properties": {"references": {"type": "array", "items": {"enum": ["Domain"]}}}},
        "Infrastructure": {"type": "object", "required": ["references"], "properties": {"references": {"type": "array", "items": {"enum": ["Domain", "Application"]}}}},
        "Api": {"type": "object", "required": ["references"], "properties": {"references": {"type": "array", "items": {"enum": ["Application", "Infrastructure"]}}}}
      }
    },
    "use_cases": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "required": ["feature", "name"], "properties": {"feature": {"type": "string"}, "name": {"type": "string"}}}, "minItems": 1},
    "arch_tests_pass": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "outbox_configured": {"type": "boolean", "const": true}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "solution_name": "Billing",
  "projects": {
    "Domain": {"references": []},
    "Application": {"references": ["Domain"]},
    "Infrastructure": {"references": ["Domain", "Application"]},
    "Api": {"references": ["Application", "Infrastructure"]}
  },
  "use_cases": [
    {"feature": "Invoices", "name": "CreateInvoice"},
    {"feature": "Invoices", "name": "GetInvoiceById"}
  ],
  "arch_tests_pass": true,
  "outbox_configured": true
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "solution_name": "billing",
  "projects": {
    "Domain": {"references": ["Infrastructure"]},
    "Application": {"references": ["Domain", "Infrastructure"]},
    "Infrastructure": {"references": ["Domain"]},
    "Api": {"references": ["Application"]}
  },
  "use_cases": [],
  "arch_tests_pass": false,
  "outbox_configured": false
}
]]></code>
    <note>solution_name not PascalCase; Domain depends on Infrastructure (inversion); Application depends on Infrastructure; no use-cases; arch tests failing; outbox missing.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>`using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore;` in the Application project.</item>
      <item>DataAnnotation `[Required]`/`[EmailAddress]` on Commands/Queries.</item>
      <item>`async void` on a MediatR `INotificationHandler&lt;T&gt;`.</item>
      <item>Aggregate collection mutated externally (`user.Posts.Add(post)` instead of `user.AddPost(post)`).</item>
      <item>`IgnoreQueryFilters()` outside an explicitly designated admin repository.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-csharp-dotnet-patterns.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
